modName: Karthspire Camp Clean Up for Tundra Defense
summary: Karthspire Camp is a really good place to set up your Outpost for 'Tundra Defense', but the forsworn tents and Hagraven Camps can get in the way. This mod just removes them, and leaves space for more, and better building placement.
descriptionHtml:
Karthspire Camp is a really good place to set up your Outpost for 'Tundra Defense', but the forsworn tents and Hagraven Camps can get in the way. This mod just removes them, and leaves space for more, and better building placement.


Contact me for any bugs or issues.
author: Mythic
